        "step": 6,
        "concept": "Deployment Considerations and Monitoring",
        "description": "Understand how threshold tuning fits into deployment decisions, including monitoring model performance over time and adjusting thresholds as data or risk profiles change. Reflect on a scenario where a fixed threshold leads to degraded performance post-deployment and how to address it.",
